{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.7","c":"هَلْ","d":"hlَْ","e":"hal"},{"b":"0.4","h":"1.2","c":"أَتَىكَ","d":"ʾatَàَkَٰ","e":"atāka"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.64","c":"حَدِيثُ","d":"ḥdَyِthُ","e":"ḥadīthu"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.23","c":"الْغَاشِيَةِ","d":"lٱغْsَٰhyِẗَِ","e":"l-ghāshiyati"}],"a":{"g":"Has there reached you the report of the Overwhelming [event]?"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وُجُوهٌ","d":"wgُjwُhٌ","e":"wujūhun"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.97","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"ywَmْʾَydِhٍ","e":"yawma-idhin"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.09","c":"خَاشِعَةٌ","d":"khsَٰhعِʿẗٌَ","e":"khāshiʿatun"}],"a":{"g":"[Some] faces, that Day, will be humbled,"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"عَامِلَةٌ","d":"عʿāَmlِẗٌَ","e":"ʿāmilatun"},{"b":"2.2","h":"2.64","c":"نَاصِبَةٌ","d":"nāَّṣbِẗٌَ","e":"nāṣibatun"}],"a":{"g":"Working [hard] and exhausted."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.78","c":"تَصْلَى","d":"tṣَlْàَٰ","e":"taṣlā"},{"b":"0.83","h":"2.08","c":"نَارًا","d":"nāَrāً","e":"nāran"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.61","c":"حَامِيَةً","d":"ḥāَmyِẗًَ","e":"ḥāmiyatan"}],"a":{"g":"They will [enter to] burn in an intensely hot Fire.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال تعالى: ﴿ تصلى نارا حامية تسقى من عين آنية ﴾ حتى إذا انقطعت أعناقهم عطشا واحترقت أجوافهم جوعا انصرف بهم إلى النار فسقوا من عين آنية قد آن حرها واشتد لفحها.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, faces [wujuh] shall be scorched by a blazing fire [nar hamiyah], given drink from a boiling spring ['ayn aniyah]. Until, when their necks are severed by thirst and their bellies are scorched by hunger, they are turned back to the Fire and given drink from a boiling spring ['ayn aniyah] whose heat has reached its peak and whose blaze has intensified.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"تُسْقَى","d":"tsُqْàَٰ","e":"tus'qā"},{"b":"0.82","h":"2.02","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِْ","e":"min"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.51","c":"عَيْنٍ","d":"عʿyَnٍْ","e":"ʿaynin"},{"b":"2.1","h":"4.11","c":"ءَانِيَةٍ","d":"ءāَnyِẗٍَ","e":"āniyatin"}],"a":{"g":"They will be given drink from a boiling spring."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"لَيْسَ","d":"lyَّsَْ","e":"laysa"},{"b":"0.62","h":"1.65","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"lhَmُْ","e":"lahum"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.63","c":"طَعَامٌ","d":"ṭعَʿāَmٌ","e":"ṭaʿāmun"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.56","c":"إِلَّا","d":"ʾilِāَّ","e":"illā"},{"b":"3.1","h":"6.27","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِ","e":"min"},{"b":"4.4","h":"7.29","c":"ضَرِيعٍ","d":"ḍrَyِعʿٍ","e":"ḍarīʿin"}],"a":{"g":"For them there will be no food except from a poisonous, thorny plant"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.3","c":"لَا","d":"lāَّ","e":"lā"},{"b":"0.37","h":"1.03","c":"يُسْمِنُ","d":"ysُmْnُِ","e":"yus'minu"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.47","c":"وَلَا","d":"wlَāَ","e":"walā"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.56","c":"يُغْنِي","d":"yغُnْàِ","e":"yugh'nī"},{"b":"2.7","h":"5.3","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِ","e":"min"},{"b":"3.8","h":"6.41","c":"جُوعٍ","d":"gjwُعʿٍ","e":"jūʿin"}],"a":{"g":"Which neither nourishes nor avails against hunger."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وُجُوهٌ","d":"wgُjwُhٌ","e":"wujūhun"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.51","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"ywَmْʾَydِhٍ","e":"yawma-idhin"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.27","c":"نَاعِمَةٌ","d":"nāَّعʿmِẗٌَ","e":"nāʿimatun"}],"a":{"g":"[Other] faces, that Day, will show pleasure."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"لِسَعْيِهَا","d":"lsِّعَʿyْhِāَ","e":"lisaʿyihā"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.87","c":"رَاضِيَةٌ","d":"rāَḍyِẗٌَ","e":"rāḍiyatun"}],"a":{"g":"With their effort [they are] satisfied"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"0.36","h":"1.06","c":"جَنَّةٍ","d":"gjnَẗٍَّ","e":"jannatin"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.31","c":"عَالِيَةٍ","d":"عʿāَlyِẗٍَ","e":"ʿāliyatin"}],"a":{"g":"In an elevated garden,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"لَا","d":"lāَّ","e":"lā"},{"b":"0.39","h":"1.37","c":"تَسْمَعُ","d":"tsَmْعَʿُ","e":"tasmaʿu"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.88","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fyِhāَ","e":"fīhā"},{"b":"2.2","h":"5.62","c":"لَاغِيَةً","d":"lغَٰyِẗًَ","e":"lāghiyatan"}],"a":{"g":"Wherein they will hear no unsuitable speech."}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fyِhāَ","e":"fīhā"},{"b":"0.74","h":"2.01","c":"عَيْنٌ","d":"عʿyَnٌْ","e":"ʿaynun"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.13","c":"جَارِيَةٌ","d":"gjāَryِẗٌَ","e":"jāriyatun"}],"a":{"g":"Within it is a flowing spring."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fyِhāَ","e":"fīhā"},{"b":"0.85","h":"2.22","c":"سُرُرٌ","d":"srُrٌُ","e":"sururun"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.19","c":"مَرْفُوعَةٌ","d":"mrَّfْwُعʿẗٌَ","e":"marfūʿatun"}],"a":{"g":"Within it are couches raised high"}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.42","c":"وَأَكْوَابٌ","d":"wʾَakَwْāَbٌ","e":"wa-akwābun"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.84","c":"مَوْضُوعَةٌ","d":"mwَّḍْwُعʿẗٌَ","e":"mawḍūʿatun"}],"a":{"g":"And cups put in place","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ثم يطأطىء رأسه فإذا أزواجه ﴿ وأكواب موضوعة ونمارق مصفوفة وزرابى مبثوثة ﴾ {} ثم اتكأ فقال: ﴿ الحمد لله الذي هدانا لهذا وما كنا لنهتدى لو لا أن هدانا الله ﴾ {} ثم ينادى مناد تحيون فلا تموتون أبدا وتقيمون فلا تظعنون أبدا وتصحون فلا تمرضون أبدا\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Then he lowers his head, and behold, his spouses, **and cups placed, and cushions arrayed, and carpets spread out.** Then he reclines and says: **\"Praise be to Allah, Who has guided us to this. And we would never have been guided if Allah had not guided us.\"** Then a caller calls out: \"You live, so you never die; and you abide, so you never depart; and you are healthy, so you never fall ill.\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.36","c":"وَنَمَارِقُ","d":"wnَmَāَrqُِ","e":"wanamāriqu"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.53","c":"مَصْفُوفَةٌ","d":"mṣَfْwُfẗٌَ","e":"maṣfūfatun"}],"a":{"g":"And cushions lined up"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَزَرَابِيُّ","d":"wzَrَāَbàُِّ","e":"wazarābiyyu"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.2","c":"مَبْثُوثَةٌ","d":"mbَtْhwُthẗٌَ","e":"mabthūthatun"}],"a":{"g":"And carpets spread around."}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"أَفَلَا","d":"ʾafَlَāَ","e":"afalā"},{"b":"0.8","h":"2.08","c":"يَنْظُرُونَ","d":"ynَẓrُwُnَ","e":"yanẓurūna"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.64","c":"إِلَى","d":"ʾilِàَ","e":"ilā"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.36","c":"الْإِبِلِ","d":"lٱʾْibِlِِ","e":"l-ibili"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.84","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kyَfَْ","e":"kayfa"},{"b":"4.5","h":"8.03","c":"خُلِقَتْ","d":"khlُqِtَْ","e":"khuliqat"}],"a":{"g":"Then do they not look at the camels - how they are created?"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.2","c":"وَإِلَى","d":"wʾَilِàَ","e":"wa-ilā"},{"b":"0.55","h":"2.1","c":"السَّمَاءِ","d":"lٱsmَّāَءِٓ","e":"l-samāi"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.82","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kyَfَْ","e":"kayfa"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.94","c":"رُفِعَتْ","d":"rfُعِʿtَْ","e":"rufiʿat"}],"a":{"g":"And at the sky - how it is raised?"}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.48","c":"وَإِلَى","d":"wʾَilِàَ","e":"wa-ilā"},{"b":"0.56","h":"1.37","c":"الْجِبَالِ","d":"lٱgْjbِāَlِ","e":"l-jibāli"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.26","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kyَfَْ","e":"kayfa"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.42","c":"نُصِبَتْ","d":"nṣُbِtَْ","e":"nuṣibat"}],"a":{"g":"And at the mountains - how they are erected?"}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.1","c":"وَإِلَى","d":"wʾَilِàَ","e":"wa-ilā"},{"b":"0.58","h":"2.02","c":"الْأَرْضِ","d":"lٱʾْarَḍِْ","e":"l-arḍi"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.53","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kyَfَْ","e":"kayfa"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.7","c":"سُطِحَتْ","d":"sṭُḥِtَْ","e":"suṭiḥat"}],"a":{"g":"And at the earth - how it is spread out?"}},"21":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"فَذَكِّرْ","d":"fdَhkَrِّْ","e":"fadhakkir"},{"b":"0.92","h":"2.27","c":"إِنَّمَا","d":"ʾinِmَّāَٓ","e":"innamā"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.54","c":"أَنْتَ","d":"ʾanَtَ","e":"anta"},{"b":"5.2","h":"7.08","c":"مُذَكِّرٌ","d":"mdُhkَrٌِّ","e":"mudhakkirun"}],"a":{"g":"So remind, [O Muhammad]; you are only a reminder."}},"22":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"لَسْتَ","d":"lsَّtَْ","e":"lasta"},{"b":"0.6","h":"1.39","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"عʿlَyَhْmِ","e":"ʿalayhim"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.94","c":"بِمُصَيْطِرٍ","d":"bmِṣُyَṭْrٍِ","e":"bimuṣayṭirin"}],"a":{"g":"You are not over them a controller."}},"23":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"إِلَّا","d":"ʾilِāَّ","e":"illā"},{"b":"0.81","h":"1.96","c":"مَنْ","d":"mnَ","e":"man"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.01","c":"تَوَلَّى","d":"twَlَàَّٰ","e":"tawallā"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.03","c":"وَكَفَرَ","d":"wkَfَrََ","e":"wakafara"}],"a":{"g":"However, he who turns away and disbelieves -"}},"24":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ","d":"fyَعُʿdَhbِّhُُ","e":"fayuʿadhibuhu"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.99","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"lٱlhَُّ","e":"l-lahu"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.43","c":"الْعَذَابَ","d":"lٱعْʿdَhāَbَ","e":"l-ʿadhāba"},{"b":"3.3","h":"6.32","c":"الْأَكْبَرَ","d":"lٱʾْakَbْrََ","e":"l-akbara"}],"a":{"g":"Then Allah will punish him with the greatest punishment."}},"25":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.5","c":"إِنَّ","d":"ʾinَِّ","e":"inna"},{"b":"1.3","h":"3.03","c":"إِلَيْنَا","d":"ʾilِyَnْāَٓ","e":"ilaynā"},{"b":"2.0","h":"6.09","c":"إِيَابَهُمْ","d":"ʾiyِāَbhَmُْ","e":"iyābahum"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, to Us is their return."}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"thmَُّ","e":"thumma"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.5","c":"إِنَّ","d":"ʾinَِّ","e":"inna"},{"b":"2.7","h":"2.74","c":"عَلَيْنَا","d":"عʿlَyَnْāَ","e":"ʿalaynā"},{"b":"3.9","h":"4.77","c":"حِسَابَهُمْ","d":"ḥsِāَbhَmُ","e":"ḥisābahum"}],"a":{"g":"Then indeed, upon Us is their account."}}}